Subject: [PATCH 100/113] fdt: Add export SoM data via FDT

Export via FDT the following data:
	board options
	board revision (major)
	product name
	serial number

Signed-off-by: Kirill Kapranov <kirill.kapranov@compulab.co.il>
---
